{"tid":188943,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"北越南 河內遊","createTime":"2017-04-06T05:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T22:59:48.000Z","uid":8833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3af485189a693a82b2281dc70a0f7d08dbe9cdd","tid":188943,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:27:28.000Z","msg":"今次一行三人一齊去越南<br />\n<strong>點解會揀越南？</strong>諗住見識多個國家既風土人情<br />\n感受下呢個地方<br />\n<br />\n首先需要整簽證，而網上簽證係最平<br />\n網上簽6USD+去到當地後比多25USD（共31USD)<br />\n<br />\n今次揀既航空公司係香港航空<br />\n<strong>點解唔揀越捷、捷星呢d？</strong><br />\n第一，時間問題，果d去到當地都11:xxpm<br />\n第二，我睇過包手提行李約HKD$1000左右<br />\n<br />\n我今次機票往越南河內除返HKD$13xx/位，除左有20KG行李<br />\n而且去到當地只係05:xx pm<br />\n相差既價錢我接受到<br />\n<br />\n出發果陣香港仲落緊毛毛雨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pg23N7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPg23N7v.jpg&h=e8b324da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n穿過雨雲後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2HDu7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2HDu7Q.jpg&h=d5c693df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次搭飛機我都好鐘意望窗外既風險<br />\n睇極都唔膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到河內，落機之後就準備兩張相同埋25USD整簽證<br />\n指示唔係好清晰，當地既人英文亦都好麻麻地<br />\n<br />\n填完表同比完錢，等左差唔多一個鐘先拎返本passport 入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網睇唔好同入境既職員有眼神接觸，有可能收你1USD先放你入境。我都無遇到，我照正常咁望，正常咁過關<br />\n<br />\n成功拎完行李入境後，就去機場度兌換店兌錢<br />\n搵左間1USD : 22,610 VND（越南盾）<br />\n最後兌左200USD即係4,522,000VND<br />\n<br />\n同買左一張300,000 VND既LTE 3.5GB淨上網卡<br />\n<br />\n就出去搵車去河內市中心<br />\n最後傾左一架車15USD直到酒店門口<br />\n<br />\n酒店一晚HKD$24x/晚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/06/132645_04c4ce43ad3eacb731aaba2b8454a30f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F06%2F132645_04c4ce43ad3eacb731aaba2b8454a30f.jpg&h=2c706126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再打"},{"pid":"c57f18ef60d29fda23e4b08b5dc9c2dd384ac592","tid":188943,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:31:59.000Z","msg":"第一晚隨便係酒店附近搵野食<br />\n<br />\n火鍋黎，個湯係辣辣地，味道一流<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/06/202009_031a8906ad66b53431c0f941e470289e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F06%2F202009_031a8906ad66b53431c0f941e470289e.jpg&h=0b580511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係d料一般，特別係魷魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似洗唔乾淨<br />\n<br />\n食完野後就附近走走<br />\n<br />\n有d騎住電單車馬伕黎聊你去sex 按摩<br />\n話有好多靚靚越南妹，我地抱住唔好蝕底，上去睇睇既心情跟住佢去<br />\n<br />\n的確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個樣唔差 身材著住衫但好豐滿，唔知係咪攝左野<br />\n開我地800,000 VND<br />\n我地純粹想望望，興趣不大<br />\n轉頭就走，佢最後話600,000 VND<br />\n但都係走左，出到門口有個操普通話既人問我地有無試<br />\n我地話無，佢話呢d係純打飛機，唔試都罷，有更好玩可以跟佢黎<br />\n<br />\n我地無理佢就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為第二日仲要早起去下龍灣<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但希望第時幫到想去既巴打"},{"pid":"3adb9b56ed7bc5e0ea8711cd2ea5878d8f87d049","tid":188943,"uid":2258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直好想去"},{"pid":"168d2e07162dd2dbaad60fefc3e26b8ed5ce2f73","tid":188943,"uid":78886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:35:44.000Z","msg":"對越南性生活更有興趣😂點解唔試下"},{"pid":"07a1a2a65ca24c8d97fd3ee3af2cc2cc28c64c26","tid":188943,"uid":2258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對越南性生活更有興趣😂點解唔試下</blockquote><br />\n入去打個飛機都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac796324f996880be19cfe9e9d92d52359dd6a0","tid":188943,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>對越南性生活更有興趣😂點解唔試下</blockquote><br />\n入去打個飛機都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想去就去馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 越南一d都唔貴<br />\n佢地d房好似病床拉個窗簾，隔離就有個人打緊飛機<br />\n好污糟既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86841461ae96662435b03a6efdd3b81ee2123cbd","tid":188943,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對越南性生活更有興趣😂點解唔試下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多好高質既越南妹<br />\n同埋好奇怪，手幼腳幼但個波好大（C以上）<br />\n<br />\n佢地咁窮無理由會去隆胸架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無越南通巴打解釋下"},{"pid":"990731283f187b3b056ecffe7cc166a8d1bee7e6","tid":188943,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:58:44.000Z","msg":"第一晚呢間酒店包埋早餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ZJ8u4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ZJ8u4d.jpg&h=4a9e6e06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二日0800am執完行李，就落去食早餐<br />\n咦喂，凍既<br />\n問佢幾點開波有早餐食，佢話0630am開始有得食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔怪得凍晒啦<br />\n<br />\n行出酒店附近搵食<br />\n越南米粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/06/234823_0a17852b06342db89d4ef66358e772ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F06%2F234823_0a17852b06342db89d4ef66358e772ca.jpg&h=5ac2e158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身諗住食河粉，言語不通叫左呢碗米<br />\n但個湯底真係一流<br />\n我地香港由細細個已經受出前一丁/合味道等味精熏陶<br />\n但係都係覺得越南既湯好正<br />\n<br />\n食飽飽等車出發去下龍灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下龍灣係玩兩日一夜，當中包左船上面訓<br />\n我一早上網訂左呢個行程，88 USD/位（呢個一般價錢，懶得去慢慢比較，如果想窮遊相信你地會比我搵到更平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n訓既係3星級船<br />\n<br />\n係度講下3星/4星船有乜分別？好多人覺得差唔多<br />\n4星船一般要110 -140 USD<br />\n通常會多個露台<br />\n有無用就見仁見智，我果架就無<br />\n見人地有果d架船真係硬件/軟件都優勝d<br />\n<br />\n富貴由人，反正都訓一晚咁多"},{"pid":"84c2eecbf3fd15cc0e1317ad1af1831ca3da58f3","tid":188943,"uid":45606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T11:38:19.000Z","msg":"巴打我煩緊去北越定南越好<br />\n你行完河內感覺點，好唔好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34dcb58345038527f026ce2caa4b1c81d21e5a4e","tid":188943,"uid":77523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:24:32.000Z","msg":"LM 黎緊想同女朋友去越南<br />\n諗緊去胡志明市定河內"},{"pid":"9bfae715294a8d841c3dde552647c91940b8ffd1","tid":188943,"uid":65599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:24:18.000Z","msg":"點解唔打埋落去下龍灣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125892b0a21bfc97044358cfb28efd38bf428c2f","tid":188943,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T19:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔打埋落去下龍灣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒撚第一次打無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9a9e4c1e6e03844b3048c80cf32c9ca53a8bcb","tid":188943,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T19:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打我煩緊去北越定南越好<br />\n你行完河內感覺點，好唔好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得 玩就唔係特別好玩<br />\n我想感受當地文化<br />\n襯後生去多幾個國家"},{"pid":"74b56098bfba53787aa0ec7741abfda42584a4ed","tid":188943,"uid":81309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T22:59:48.000Z","msg":"Sim卡仲有幾多gb揀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}